shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n民主黨立法會議員許智峯亦於早上11時許進入理大校園，並向記者稱會在內視察一下情況。"},{"pid":"9b80bc5d8f9c7705adaa2149005541221e66ccfc","tid":1758523,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T07:09:02.000Z","msg":"推行動post. <br />\nBe water. <br />\n遍地開花<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可"},{"pid":"b255836aa5a8e724ba34815e21ac6712b971596c","tid":1758523,"uid":44559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T07:11:53.000Z","msg":"擺明知無曬 幫佢D狗落台LA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d0a400aaaa21faab2cc7fd4f77e26663eac9df5","tid":1758523,"uid":189283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f227ac77c6a03980400334ab2604e7654eaa6348","tid":1758523,"uid":218699,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"f1f3827b2b263748b111ee63f69e74ed85e635c9","tid":1758523,"uid":335434,"like":72,"dislike":0,"score":72,"quote":{"pid":"ce99a61bc05fabba4e7be8f09bcab2a5e1699ae4","tid":1758523,"uid":1903,"like":34,"dislike":2,"score":32,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:09:07.000Z","msg":"咩事咁強硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:15:47.000Z","msg":"Poly本身有十幾億擴建撥款 依家俾班保皇狗同政府玩到無撚咗 發窮惡都好撚正常啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T07:03:40.000Z","msg":"啱呀 奶你又冇錢 又開唔返學 仲唔屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T07:14:49.000Z","msg":"唔開sem都要照收學費，賺到fatfat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c47a94f9a51cb9820eb470f819a5604cd58c3cb","tid":1758523,"uid":235501,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9d0a400aaaa21faab2cc7fd4f77e26663eac9df5","tid":1758523,"uid":189283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f227ac77c6a